    "description": "Reliance Retail invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Department Manager at our Patna location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Reliance Retail:\nReliance Retail is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Retail!",
